commit_message: Renamed pushproperty! variable names to better reflect terminology
Added support for the join operator, and more documentation
Updated README to include new features
Added a plasmid to example.gbk for testing
Added ability to read/write feature lines with order(...)

Fixed delete! bug and added convert method for Locus
Added support for broadcasted setindex! for GeneDataViews
